  "content": "<p><a href=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-attachment-id=\"191\" data-permalink=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/2009/11/24/some-respec/img_0541/\" data-orig-file=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2816,2112\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;2.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon PowerShot SD600&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1259059635&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;5.8&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.016666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_0541\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=1024\" src=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=500&#038;h=375\" alt=\"\" title=\"IMG_0541\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-191\" srcset=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=500&amp;h=375 500w, https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=750 1000w, https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0541.jpg?w=768&amp;h=576 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>I consider this a combination of feng shui and a jackhammer. or a T-rex. </p>\n<p>Its my take on what energy looks like.<br />\n<a href=\"https://inpixels09.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/img_0546.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-attachment-id=\"192\" data-